to be close to you

348
00:29:49.799 --> 00:29:50.960
except me.

349
00:29:54.680 --> 00:29:55.720
And...

350
00:29:56.200 --> 00:29:58.079
And I'm just a guy

351
00:30:00.480 --> 00:30:03.519
