353
00:30:12.559 --> 00:30:13.599
Tan.

354
00:30:22.400 --> 00:30:25.039
The question you've
all been waiting for.

355
00:30:25.039 --> 00:30:28.880
Who started flirting first?

356
00:30:32.720 --> 00:30:34.720
