360
00:30:48.519 --> 00:30:51.440
I'm about to do
the most important thing in my life.

361
00:30:51.880 --> 00:30:53.240
But I don't know
if I'll be able to pull it off.

362
00:30:58.640 --> 00:30:59.680
Then,

363
00:31:00.359 --> 00:31:02.279
